class_name KidBasil
extends PartyMember

## Basil as a kid — the prologue's playable body. No kit at all: the childhood
## chapter's verbs are walk / hop / interact (the world before the Ebb was
## safe — combat and the laser gun arrive with the adult chapters). Movement,
## the hop and the hurt stagger all live in PartyMember; the interact verb
## lives with the things being interacted with (NPCs, quest pickups).
